<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:21:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：消息人士称，美国调查发现中国不公平地主导造船业，为处罚铺平道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-probe-finds-china-unfairly-dominates-shipbuilding-paving-way-penalties-2025-01-13/</link><description>三名熟悉为期数月贸易调查结果的消息人士告诉路透社，美国总统乔·拜登政府得出的结论是，中国利用不公平的政策和做法来主导全球海事、物流和造船行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-probe-finds-china-unfairly-dominates-shipbuilding-paving-way-penalties-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>印度4月至12月成品钢材进口量至少触及六年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-december-finished-steel-imports-touch-least-six-year-high-2025-01-13/</link><description>路透社周一查阅的临时政府数据显示，在 2024 年 4 月开始的财政年度的前 9 个月，印度成品钢材进口量创下至少六年来的新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:58:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-december-finished-steel-imports-touch-least-six-year-high-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>分析师表示，随着矿山关闭、中国电动汽车销售缓解过剩局面，锂价将于 2025 年稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-prices-stabilise-2025-mine-closures-china-ev-sales-ease-glut-analysts-2025-01-13/</link><description>分析师和交易商表示，由于中国关闭的矿山和强劲的电动汽车销售消化了供应过剩，锂价在经历了两年的大幅下跌后，预计将在 2025 年企稳，尽管矿山重新开放的可能性可能会限制涨幅。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:36:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-prices-stabilise-2025-mine-closures-china-ev-sales-ease-glut-analysts-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：忘掉软着陆，继续飞翔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-01-13/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:33:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>总理表示格林纳达从与中国的关系中受益匪浅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/grenada-has-benefited-greatly-ties-with-china-prime-minister-says-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国官方媒体周一援引格林纳达总理的话说，格林纳达从与中国的关系中受益匪浅，并期待加强与这个亚洲国家的合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:27:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/grenada-has-benefited-greatly-ties-with-china-prime-minister-says-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国军事代表团将于1月中旬访问日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-delegation-visit-japan-mid-january-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国国防部周一表示，经两国同意，中国军队代表将于一月中旬访问日本，以增进相互“理解和信任”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-delegation-visit-japan-mid-january-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>AI芯片需求旺盛，台积电第四季度利润跃升58%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-fourth-quarter-profit-seen-jumping-58-strong-ai-chip-demand-2025-01-13/</link><description>台积电是全球人工智能应用先进芯片的主要生产商，由于需求激增，预计周四第四季度利润将跃升 58%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:16:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-fourth-quarter-profit-seen-jumping-58-strong-ai-chip-demand-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>对美国对俄罗斯能源利益新制裁的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/reactions-new-us-sanctions-against-russian-energy-interests-2025-01-13/</link><description>美国财政部周五宣布对俄罗斯能源行业实施全面新制裁，其中包括石油巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司(Gazprom Neft)和苏尔古特石油天然气公司(Surgutneftegaz)，以试图阻止莫斯科与乌克兰的战争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/reactions-new-us-sanctions-against-russian-energy-interests-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示，美国、日本、菲律宾领导人讨论了中国在南海的行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-japanese-philippine-leaders-discussed-chinas-behavior-south-china-sea-white-2025-01-13/</link><description>白宫表示，美国总统乔·拜登周日与日本和菲律宾外长进行了虚拟会面，以推进这三个国家之间的合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-japanese-philippine-leaders-discussed-chinas-behavior-south-china-sea-white-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告涉嫌中国间谍活动“显着增加”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-significant-rise-suspected-chinese-espionage-2025-01-13/</link><description>台湾国家安全局表示，去年被指控为中国从事间谍活动的台湾人增加了三分之一，达到 64 人，其中大多数是现役或退役士兵。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-significant-rise-suspected-chinese-espionage-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>贸易紧张局势下中国出口加速，进口意外</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-quickens-amid-trade-risks-imports-surprise-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国12月份的出口增长势头强劲，进口也出现复苏，不过年底的强劲增长在一定程度上是由于工厂在特朗普担任总统期间为应对贸易风险加剧而向海外大量库存所推动的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-quickens-amid-trade-risks-imports-surprise-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国加强政策措施捍卫脆弱的人民币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-steps-up-policy-measures-defend-fragile-yuan-2025-01-13/</link><description>周一，在人民币兑强势美元徘徊于16个月低点附近之际，中国加大了政策措施力度，放宽允许更多离岸借款的规定，并发出口头警告，以捍卫人民币疲软。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-steps-up-policy-measures-defend-fragile-yuan-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和日本外长将在首尔政治动荡中会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-amid-political-turmoil-seoul-2025-01-13/</link><description>韩国和日本外长将于周一在韩国首都举行会谈，美国的主要盟友寻求在首尔数十年来最严重的政治危机中强调改善关系和共同的安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-amid-political-turmoil-seoul-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2025-01-13/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 02:51:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>开发商收到清算申请后中国世茂股价下跌15%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-drops-15-after-developer-receives-liquidation-petition-2025-01-13/</link><description>在收到清算申请后，中国世茂集团的股价周一下跌 15%，至 0.73 港元，为 9 月 26 日以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 01:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-drops-15-after-developer-receives-liquidation-petition-2025-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>